    .info(href="#") i

  .details
    h2 About Sampleton
    p.
      Sampleton is a Web App to streamline biological surveying. It is meant to be a fieldwork and lab companion,
      facilitatng data entry and providing instant feedback.
    p Sampleton is not yet released, but feel free to try out the demo by simply signing in.
    p.email
      a(href="mailto:hello@sampleton.net") hello@sampleton.net

